fields.name: EncryptionComplianceStatus
fields.description: Describes whether the search service is compliant or not with respect to having non customer encrypted resources. If a service has more than one non customer encrypted resource and 'Enforcement' is 'enabled' then the service will be marked as 'nonCompliant'.

fields.name: Enforcement
fields.description: Describes how a search service should enforce having one or more non customer encrypted resources.
